- 📈 "AI agency" is becoming crowded — niche specialization is MANDATORY
- ⚙ Client communication across timezones requires discipline
- 💰 First 2–3 months may have zero revenue while building pipeline
- 🌊 USD/INR exchange rate fluctuations (minor risk)
- 👥 US recession can freeze spending (mitigate by targeting SMBs, not enterprises)

