**One-liner:** Build AI solutions at Indian cost, sell at US prices — the INR/USD arbitrage plus time-zone advantage is India's biggest superpower for tech services.

**Why it's SAFE:**
- AI demand is EXPLODING — every US business wants AI but can't afford US agencies
- Skills are learnable — Claude, GPT APIs, LangChain make AI development accessible
- Dollar revenue protects against Indian inflation
- Even 3 clients at $3,000/month = ₹7.5L/month — life-changing income
- Portfolio effect — each project becomes a case study for the next client

**India Advantage:** Indian developer costs 5–10x less than US. English proficiency enables direct client communication. Time zone means overnight delivery (client's morning = your evening). India produces 1.5M+ engineering graduates yearly — talent pool is deep.

**Step-by-Step to First ₹:**

```
Day 1–3:     Pick ONE niche. Best options for beginners:
             - AI chatbot for e-commerce stores (Shopify)
             - AI content automation for marketing agencies
             - AI document summarizer for law firms
             - AI data dashboard for small businesses

Day 4–10:    Build ONE impressive demo project. Use OpenAI/Anthropic API + 
             simple web frontend. Record a 3-minute Loom video walking through it.
             This demo is your portfolio — it MUST look professional.

Day 11–15:   Optimize LinkedIn profile. Headline: "I Build AI [specific thing]
             for [specific industry]". NOT "AI Developer | ML | Data Science."
             Post 3 times about your demo and the problem it solves.

Day 16–30:   Send 50 cold LinkedIn messages per day (use LinkedIn Sales Navigator
             free trial). Target: Founders/CMOs/Ops managers at US SMBs in your
             chosen niche. Message: "I built [demo] that does [specific thing]
             for [their industry]. 2-min video: [link]. Worth a look?"

Day 31–45:   From 750 messages, expect 30–50 replies, 5–10 calls, 1–3 clients.
             First client: offer 50% discount for video testimonial.

Day 46–60:   Deliver first project. Overdeliver. Get video testimonial.
             Raise price to full rate for client #2 and #3.

Month 3–6:   3–5 clients at $2,000–5,000/month each.
