- ⚠️ Don't take on projects outside your niche to make money — one bad delivery in an unfamiliar domain ruins your reputation and confidence
- ⚠️ Always have a clear scope document before starting — US clients will add "one more thing" forever. Scope creep kills profitability
- ⚠️ Set realistic timelines — promising 1 week and delivering in 3 weeks is worse than promising 3 weeks and delivering in 2

